doc: When I try to add any website or any user, i am not able to do it.

'Loading Data...' comes written, but it doesnt go beyond that. The 'Loading Data' screen stays there, and you have to hit the back button of the browser to stop it, and no new user or website is getting added.

Any possible cause, and troubleshooting steps for this. i dont want to reinstall Piwik. It is currently being used by users on our websites, so any debugging/troubleshooting steps would be very helpfule.
